OL,3,CPrison officer pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cmisconduct after sex with inmate in
OL,5,Ccell
OL,7,FA prison officer has pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fmisconduct after having sex with an
OL,9,Finmate in a cell.
OL,11,FLinda De Sousa Abreu, 30, of Fulham,
OL,12,Fsouth-west London, was charged after a
OL,13,Fvideo of the activity was shared on
OL,14,Fsocial media.
OL,16,FA police investigation was launched
OL,17,Fafter officers were made aware of a
OL,18,Fvideo filmed inside HMP Wandsworth in
OL,19,Fsouth London.
