OL,7,FDe Sousa Abreu was arrested and
OL,8,Fcharged with misconduct in public
OL,9,Foffice.
OL,11,FShe wore a light-coloured suit and
OL,12,Fbrown top for the short hearing at
OL,13,FIsleworth Crown Court in west London.
OL,15,FThe charge states that De Sousa Abreu
OL,16,F"wilfully and without reasonable
OL,17,Fexcuse or justification misconducted
OL,18,Fyourself in a way which amounted to an
OL,19,Fabuse of the public's trust in the
OL,20,Foffice holder by engaging in a sexual
OL,21,Fact with a prisoner in a prison cell".
