OL,7,FIt happened at Wandsworth between June
OL,8,F26-28.
OL,10,FThe mother was arrested at Heathrow
OL,11,FAirport and was due to catch a flight
OL,12,Fto Madrid having notified the prison
OL,13,Fof her travel plans.
OL,15,FDe Sousa Abreu, who holds a Portuguese
OL,16,Fpassport, was granted conditional
OL,17,Fbail, and will next appear at
OL,18,FIsleworth Crown Court on November 7.
